race.comment: RITZY ETHICS (1) has a strong record here with two wins and a minor from six starts. Missed the frame latest (30.27) when fifth over 520m at this track in a Grade 5. Expected to be in the finish. MAGICAL ANG (3) goes very well this course and distance starting seven times for four wins and two minors. Below best last time at this track (30.60) in a NG, finishing a 13 length sixth. Makes strong appeal on best. MRS. BUTTONS (2) was a winner (29.97) at Richmond two back but out of the placings last time when 6th at this track. Can figure in the finish. VINTAGE FLAIR (8) was out of the money here last time out but can bounce back.
